-------------------------
---- PC INSTALLATION ----
-------------------------

To install Zinc Application Framework on systems running DOS, Windows, or 
OS/2, insert the first "Zinc Engine" diskette into the desired drive
(e.g., drive A) and type:

  a:<Enter>
  install<Enter>

The installation program will ask you to select the drive to install
to as well as which parts of the Framework you wish to install. 
Please refer to "Chapter 2-Installation" of the Programmer's Guide
for more information on installation procedures.


----------------------------
---- MOTIF INSTALLATION ----
----------------------------

The file 'motif.txt' explains how to install Zinc on workstations
and other systems running Motif.


